      "span_text": "Functional images were obtained using a 3-D PRESTO-SENSE pulse sequence  with shimmed background and the following parameters: repetition time = 22.5 msec, echo time = 33.2 msec, flip angle = 10°, field of view = 224 × 256 × 160, matrix = 56 × 64 × 40, voxel size = 4 mm isotropic, scan time = 0.6075 sec, 40 slices (sagittal orientation).",
